
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-bellis-dnsop-connection-close-00.txt'>
    <title>"Connection Close Signalling for DNS", Ray Bellis</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-bellis-dnsop-connection-close-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document updates [RFC6891] by specifying a new single-bit flag in a DNS response that when seen in a packet carried over a connection-orientated transport protocol indicates to the client that it should close the current connection.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-10-24T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
